  "prompt": "Which is a good inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Coffee County AL?",
  "response": "For those seeking inpatient drug and alcohol rehab centers near Coffee County, AL, one can consider several options. While I don't have real-time databases to pull the latest information, here are a few possibilities that can be explored:\n\n1. **Southeast Health** - Located in nearby Dothan, Alabama, Southeast Health offers various behavioral health services, including support for substance abuse.\n\n2. **The Haven** - Also in Dothan, The Haven provides inpatient rehabilitation services that might be suitable for those dealing with substance abuse issues.\n\n3. **SpectraCare Health Systems** - This facility offers various mental health and substance abuse services, including inpatient treatment programs, and has multiple locations in the region.\n\n4. **Bradford Health Services** - Though not directly in Coffee County, Bradford has several locations across Alabama, providing comprehensive addiction treatment services.\n\nIt's important to contact these facilities directly to inquire about their specific programs, availability, and whether they meet your specific needs. Additionally, seeking a consultation with a healthcare provider or a counselor may help in identifying the most appropriate facility based on individual circumstances.",
